[[File:Elisabeth Grieg - Norges Bank Årstale (192750).jpg|thumbnail|Grieg in 2016]] '''Elisabeth Grieg''' (born 12 June 1959) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[businessperson]].
She is part owner of [[Grieg Group]] and holds many chair and board positions in the group. Outside the group she is Chairman of [[Norsk Hydro]] since 2007, deputy chair of the [[Norwegian Shipowners' Association]] and member of the board of [[StatoilHydro]]. Elisabeth Grieg is a member of the [[advisory board]] of the [[Sahara Forest Project]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://saharaforestproject.com/foundation/advisory-board.html |title=Sahara Forest Project: Advisory board |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014084125/http://saharaforestproject.com/foundation/advisory-board.html |archivedate=2013-10-14 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.proff.no/proff/search/roleDetails.c?freeText=Elisabeth+Grieg&id=106727 |title=Rollesøk - Elisabeth Grieg |author=Proff.no |accessdate=2008-05-18}}</ref>
